data.description: HAVE YOU BEEN LOOKING FOR A 4 BEDROOM HOME THAT IS HAS A TRANQUIL FEEL BUT IS MINUTES TO I10?  YOUR HOME HAS HIT THE MARKET.  PULLING UP TO THIS CHARMER YOU WILL SEE THE PRIDE OF OWNERSHIP.  WALKING IN THE FOYER IS FLANKED BY A FORMAL DINING ROOM AND WHAT COULD BE USED AS A FORMAL LIVING OR STUDY THE FAMILY ROOM IS OPEN TO THE KITHCEN AND FEATURES HIGH CEILINGS.  CHECK OUT THE BEAUTIFUL TILE FLOORING.  THIS IS PERFECT FOR PETS OR CHILDREN.  THE KITCHEN FEATURES A BUMP UP BAR FOR MORNING COFFEE OR AFTERNOON HOMEWORK.  THERE ARE A TON OF CABINETS AND A PANTRY FOR EXTRA STORAGE.  THERE IS EVEN AN EAT IN AREA.  THE LARGE MASTER BEDROOM IS SPLIT FROM THE ADDITIONAL BEDROOMS.  IT FEATURES A HUGE WALK IN CLOSET, DOUBLE VANITY, A SEPARATE SHOWER AND A GARDEN TUB.  THE ADDITIONAL BEDROOMS ARE ALL NICE SIZED AND HAVE GREAT CLOSET SPACE.  THE FENCED BACKYARD IS A PERFECT OASIS.  THERE IS A LARGE SCREEN PORCH FOR EVENING SUMMER DINNERS.  IF YOU LOVE FISHING, THERE IS EASY ACCESS TO WATER. CALL TODAY TO SEE THIS AWESOME HOME!!!!
